---
// Services.astro - Secci√≥n de servicios tipo mockup
---

<section id="services" class="w-full min-h-screen flex flex-col bg-white justify-center items-center p-0 m-0">
  <div class="w-full max-w-7xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-12 md:py-0 min-h-screen">
    <!-- Columna izquierda: Imagen -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-[65%] flex flex-col items-start justify-center mb-10 md:mb-0 -ml-0 md:-ml-24 lg:-ml-40 -mr-0 md:-mr-12 lg:-mr-24">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-light mb-10 text-left w-full pl-0 md:pl-12 lg:pl-24">
        Our <span class="font-bold">Services</span>
      </h2>
      <img
        src="/services.png"
        alt="Services"
        class="w-full h-64 md:h-[400px] lg:h-[480px] object-cover shadow"
        style="border-radius:0;"
      />
    </div>
    <!-- Columna derecha: Texto -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center items-start md:pl-16">
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light text-black mb-8 text-left">
        Bring your vision to life through <span class="font-bold">web, mobile, and desktop solutions</span>
      </p>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light text-black text-left">
        Crafted <span class="font-bold">fast</span> and <span class="font-bold">reliably</span>, by a <span class="font-bold">new generation of developers</span>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 